title: Chile Money Supply M2
description: Money Supply M2 in Chile increased to 179811.51 CLP Billion in October from 179598.48 CLP Billion in September of 2022. Money Supply M2 in Chile averaged 51134.07 CLP Billion from 1986 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 179811.51 CLP Billion in October of 2022 and a record low of 753.67 CLP Billion in January of 1986. Chile Money Supply M2 includes M1 plus short-term time deposits in banks. This page provides - Chile Money Supply M2 - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Chile
